              "content": "=Job Title: {{ $json.title }}\nCompany: {{ $json.company }}\nDescription: {{ $json.description }}\nApply Link: {{ $json.apply_link }}\nPosted: {{ $json.posted }}\nSalary: {{ $json.salary }}\n\nScore this job."
            },
            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "You are a job scoring assistant.\n\nScore this job from 1-10 based on fit for this candidate:\n\nSkills: Python, SQL, RAG pipelines, LangChain, FastAPI, Flask, React, n8n, Make.com, Pinecone, PostgreSQL, AWS\nExperience: 2 years as AI Engineer at High Five Media. Built LLM systems, RAG pipelines, automation tools, HubSpot integrations, OCR tools, and AI chatbots. MS in Computer Science from University of Oklahoma.\nLevel: Junior to Mid (2-3 years experience)\nTarget roles: AI Engineer, AI Automation Engineer, Full Stack AI\nAvoid: \n- Roles requiring more than 5 years experience\n- Roles requiring PhD or advanced degree\n- Roles requiring security clearance\n- Internships\n- Staffing agencies\n\nScoring guide:\n- 9-10: Perfect match, 0-3 years required, strong skill overlap\n- 7-8: Good match, 3-5 years required, most skills match\n- 5-6: Partial match, some skills missing or slightly senior\n- Below 5: Poor fit, too senior, wrong skills, or requires clearance\n\nIMPORTANT: If a job requires 5+ years or 8+ years experience, score it below 5.\nReturn ONLY this exact format, no extra text, no markdown:\n{\"score\": 7, \"reason\": \"one sentence explanation\"}"
            }
          ]
